## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Major Architecture Decision**: This transformation will completely replace the current terminal-based UI with a Google-style interface. The terminal concept will be preserved only in the "Terminal-style CLI Resume" themed page.

> [!WARNING]
> **Breaking Changes**: 
> - Complete UI/UX overhaul from terminal to Google-style
> - New backend required (FastAPI)
> - New database required
> - Existing components will be refactored or replaced

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Technology Stack Confirmation**:
> - **Frontend**: React + Tailwind CSS (existing) + new components
> - **Backend**: FastAPI (new)
> - **Database**: SQLite (local dev) / PostgreSQL (Supabase/Neon for production)
> - **AI**: RAG-based system with embeddings (sentence-transformers or OpenAI embeddings)
> - **Voice**: Web Speech API (browser-based, free) or external APIs
> - **Deployment**: Vercel (frontend) + Render/Railway (backend)

> [!CAUTION]
> **AI System Limitations**: 
> - Free-tier AI hosting has rate limits
> - Voice synthesis quality varies by provider
> - RAG system requires initial setup and indexing

