### Component 3: AI System (RAG-based)

#### [NEW] [backend/ai/](file:///c:/Users/Srish/Desktop/srishti_portfolio/backend/ai/)
- `knowledge_base.py`: Vector store management, indexing, and retrieval
- `embeddings.py`: Text embedding generation (sentence-transformers)
- `chat_handler.py`: ChatGPT-style response generation
- `search_handler.py`: AI-powered search functionality
- `voice_handler.py`: Speech-to-Text and Text-to-Speech integration

**AI System Architecture**:
```mermaid
graph LR
    A[User Query] --> B[Embedding Generator]
    B --> C[Vector Store]
    C --> D[Retrieval]
    D --> E[Context Builder]
    E --> F[LLM/Response Generator]
    F --> G[Response]
    
    H[Admin Update] --> I[Re-indexing Trigger]
    I --> C
```

**Knowledge Sources**:
- Resume (structured data + PDF text)
- Projects (title, description, tech stack, links)
- Skills (categories, proficiency)
- Experience (company, role, achievements)
- Blogs (content, tags, metadata)

