**API Endpoints**:

**Authentication**:
- `POST /api/auth/login` - Admin login
- `POST /api/auth/refresh` - Refresh JWT token

**Public Data**:
- `GET /api/public/profile` - Get personal info
- `GET /api/public/projects` - Get all projects
- `GET /api/public/skills` - Get all skills
- `GET /api/public/experience` - Get experience & education
- `GET /api/public/blogs` - Get all blog posts
- `GET /api/public/resume` - Get resume data

**Admin (Protected)**:
- `PUT /api/admin/profile` - Update personal info
- `POST /api/admin/projects` - Create project
- `PUT /api/admin/projects/:id` - Update project
- `DELETE /api/admin/projects/:id` - Delete project
- (Similar CRUD for skills, experience, blogs, resume)

**AI**:
- `POST /api/ai/chat` - Send chat message, get response
- `POST /api/ai/search` - AI-powered search
- `POST /api/ai/voice/transcribe` - Speech-to-text
- `POST /api/ai/voice/synthesize` - Text-to-speech

**Health**:
- `GET /api/health` - Health check endpoint

